Audit Manager - International Banking Institution A leading International Bank that pride themselves on offering Fantastic Career progression & having approachable senior-level management are currently on a recruitment drive & seeking Audit Managers for the following Audit teams:
-Retail / Consumer Banking Audit -Credit Risk Audit -Private Banking / Wealth Audit -Technology Audit (IT Infrastructure Audit / Information Security Audit) - CISA preferred here -Country Audit
Responsibilities -To carry out risk assessments and audit engagements of varying business units and deliver the audit plan in cooperation with the Functional Teams. -Risk assessment responsibility -Establish relationships with Stakeholders including business unit managers -Report internal audit engagements to established standards and timelines.
Qualifications & Skills Key Attributes -Either knowledge of professional auditing or business knowledge with core audit / business skills. -Professional audit certification would be a nice to have. -Ability to commit to > 40% business travel.
Singapore Registration No: R1436061 EA Licence No: 11C5854
Astbury Marsden - Asia Pacific
Astbury Marsden specialises in recruiting uniquely talented people with experience in business technology, organisational change, regulatory and assurance functions and specialist technical skills.
